Dialogue: 2,0:02:11.99,0:02:17.91,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an4\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(84,110)}The Valley of the Welling Tide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! That guy came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know he wasn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your leg injury had weakened you \Nand caused you to pass out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband found you and carried you \Nback to our home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to thank him for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to till our land on the mountain slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't be back until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to rush me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you something to fill you up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I've entered paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hold yourself back. Eat your fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that a green field of rice I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, couldn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the middle of winter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:03:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that the sound of a hoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is someone outside tilling at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello, Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your leg better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your husband hasn't returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he came back around dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but he left again right after breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the fields out back at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't imagine it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it possible spring came without my realizing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, don't tell me I'm actually still out there \Nfreezing to death and this is all just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you probably shouldn't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had a rough time, so feel free to rest here as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, these rice paddies are very impressive, especially given the time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just work on them nonstop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He gives off a sweet scent...{uh oh}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So you didn't do anything special?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of endurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can work day and night without feeling a bit of fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider these rice paddies as the fruits of my labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This scent...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it kouki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was this scent, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, I made tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll take a break, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be taking it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the husband's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.29,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I take it that his mother is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She passed away a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost her about a year after she gave birth to your son, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the circumstances of her death were strange, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to be a mushi-shi, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy for me to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believe your son may be under the influence of mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there other details you'd care to share with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If my hunch is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the lives of both your son and your daughter-in-law are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi-shi or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't have you saying anything untoward to my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to repay our kindness by doing us harm, please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ever tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Come, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't finish your vegetables again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to become tough like your dad, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better clean your plate, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it. Attaboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, can I have more?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look who's suddenly eager!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're a mushi-shi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's this important thing you have to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get more rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone far beyond your body's natural limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for your concern, but I'm fine, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been this way for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can barely get a good night's rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My body gets restless when I try to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back out in the fields before I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you're likely unaware of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a mushi that's responsible for all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong. It's my free will that's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, this place was just a desolate, empty valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've toiled for years to transform it into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked day and night, day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who made the valley into what it is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a better life for my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make sure they'd never suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this came from what {\i1}I{\i0} wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you still want it if you knew it was built on the sacrifice of your mother's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you not to say anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in his own best interests to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not your decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't interfere any further \Nwith this family,{Comma for dramatic emphasis} or this valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Houichi, are you going to \Ntill the fields on the slopes again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want another paddy ready to go by spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What you heard earlier today... Is it bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After she gave birth to me, \Nshe grew weaker and died, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who took Mom from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly why I have to keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Houichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for stepping over the line earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a mushi purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Should there come a time when you feel it's necessary, feel free to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right before.{Technically, this should be a colon, but meh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right \Nto take away this valley's prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come inside soo—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in pain at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you should stay and rest awhile, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. I just got careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, you're working too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Houichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a seat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you all mind giving us some privacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to take this tale to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here now, Houichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be hungry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, you're still unable to produce milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because I haven't been able to feed you properly either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, the valley was flush with new immigrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so everyone was barely scraping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No one could afford to share their milk with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we were at our wits' end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.81,0:14:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't find Houichi some milk soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sweet smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That pond is pure white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You suckled on it with single-minded intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And the following day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo finally started producing milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that white water was some kind of medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never found that white pond again, no matter how much we searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.21,0:15:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You drank your mother's milk and grew steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However, almost as if in counter to your growth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo's health deteriorated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face looks really pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm producing a lot of milk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... breast milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I sought out doctors far and wide for {help or even just }answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but not one of them believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, around the time you were to be weaned...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't ever tell him about my illness... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him to be happy, \Nso he mustn't know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've liked to have watched over him, \Nbut I don't think I'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be all right, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me, Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet even with her last breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,your mother wished only for your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So my body grew this strong \Nbecause I suckled the blood of my own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What caused you to do that \Nwas a Chishio, or "Milk Tide" mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chishio is a parasite \Nthat seeks out a newborn to be its host{Timing: Join if you'd like. I'd prefer it, but I didn't check the audio length or the line length.}{i'd like to, but 126 characters...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and then turns the bodily fluids of the newborn's mother into milk for its own nourishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,As the host matures,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it starts to exude a particular scent \Nthat promotes the growth of nearby plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.49,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chishio then pushes its host \Nto neglect sleep and keep eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,focusing on building its own strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once its host collapses from exhaustion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Chishio leaves its host \Nand ensnares yet another infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So these rice paddies were all thanks to the mushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, {\i1}you're{\i0} the one who actually cultivated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If or when you decide to take the mushi purge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,just let your dad know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot give up this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer an infant who needs someone to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I, too, have a family I must protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.01,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it means I must use \Nthe same power that killed my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mom. I only ever bring you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:21:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyo, he's become a fine father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Milk turns to blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nourishes the earth, and then returns to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the earth is imbued with a living, welling tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.67,0:21:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Several years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the valley came to endure \Nthe first of several harsh winters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. We're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But even now, the valley \Nechoes with laughter and joy.
